Hi Chad.  It&#39;s great to see others giving this method a try.  I&#39;ve been working with this technique going on three years now.  It takes forever and a day to go through the video one frame at a time, so whenever I share, I always just provide the still captures of the images I find.

Interestingly, two of my ITC images have been verified by a forensic lab as being a match to the photograph of the person taken while they were still in the physical.  Kinda cool.  :-)

I&#39;d love to take a peek at the images you got once you&#39;re done going through the video and clipping them out.  I actually saw some while looking at your video (I kept hitting the stop button randomly).  I tried to find your posted still images, but don&#39;t see them.  LOL, probably &quot;operator error&quot; on my part!

Margaret

